Executive Profile
James A. Varilek  Executive Vice President and President of Chlor Alkali Vinyls & Services, Olin CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 2 different industries.59$1,815,675As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. James A. Varilek, also known as Jim, has been Executive Vice President at Olin Corporation since October 5, 2015. Mr. Varilek has been President of Chlor Alkali Vinyls and Services at olin corporation since October 5, 2015. In this role, he led the Chlor-Alkali and Vinyl Business and organizational readiness for the Dow Chlorine Products divestiture. He served as Chief Operating Officer of Dow Chlorine Products. He served as Chief Executive Officer and President ... of Union Carbide Corporation. He holds a bachelor's degree in Economics and a master's degree in Business Administration from the University of Michigan.Read Full Background




